D

dag - package dag
The package that implements a directed oriented graph.
data - package data
The package that manipulates the data from the data files.
Data - Interface in data
The interface Data handles with the data from input files, and its methods are associated with reading operations that allow the user to manipulate the data from a specific .csv file with the input format considered for this project.
DataTest - Class in data
The class DataTest is an implementation of the interface Data that handles with the testing data file.
DataTest(String) - Constructor for class data.DataTest
The constructor creates an element of the type DataTest that includes the number or random variables, the number of events and an element of type TimeSample.
DataTrain - Class in data
The class DataTrain is an implementation of the interface Data that handles with the training data file.
DataTrain(String) - Constructor for class data.DataTrain
The constructor creates an element of the type DataTrain that includes the number or random variables, the number of events and a 2-D array of type TimeSample.
Destination<T> - Class in dag
Subclass of Node that represents a node as being the destination of another node (one or more Origin node point to it - it's parents)
